title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today’s Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last nights Browns/Steelers game. Hall of Famer Ed Reed tells us who his enemy was during his playing days. Sports Illustrated's Chris Mannix discusses Ime Udoka's suspension.
